fields.name: Red Rover Chew Buddy
fields.description: Unleash the fun with Fetch & Feast's Red Rover Chew Buddy — a canine delight that combines style, durability, and playfulness for your furry best friend. This meticulously designed red dog-shaped chew toy is more than just a plaything; it's a statement of quality and joy in every wagging tail.

fields.name: Fetch & Feast Premium Chicken Feast for Adult Dogs (10kg)
fields.description: Indulge your four-legged friend in the epitome of canine cuisine with Fetch & Feast™ Premium Chicken Delight. Specifically formulated for adult dogs, this 10kg bag of exquisite dry food is a culinary masterpiece that seamlessly blends nutrition and flavor. Featuring real chicken as its star ingredient, our premium dry food ensures a protein-rich and well-balanced diet for your beloved pet. Carefully selected ingredients work together to provide essential nutrients, supporting your dog's overall well-being, from a glossy coat to robust muscles and sustained energy levels.
